T1  - Concealing and confounding adverse signals: insider wealth-maximizing behavior in the IPO process
AU  - Ang, James S.
AU  - Brau, James C.
JO  - Journal of Financial Economics
VL  - 67
IS  - 1
SP  - 149
EP  - 172
PY  - 2003
DA  - 2003/01/01/
